== Usage ==
This template uses a parser function to create the table start and finish. The general syntax is:
<pre><nowiki>{{Japanese Phrasebook entry|begin}}
{{Japanese Phrasebook entry
 | english = 
 | romaji  = 
 | japanese= 
}}
...
{{Japanese Phrasebook entry|end}}</nowiki></pre>

